title: Test failure in pytorch/test/onnx/test_models.py
body_html:
Issue description

I have built Pytorch from yesterday's (Sept 25th) master. It is a CPU-only release build on Ubuntu 16.04. More details are given below.

I am trying to run the pytorch/test/onnx/test_models.py test, but it fails to export PixelShuffle op in the SuperResolution.py model.

Code example

cd pytorch/test/onnx
python test_models.py

I see the following failure:
